## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Python 3.8 or higher
- pip (Python package manager)

### Installation

1. **Clone the repository**
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/mini-crm-dashboard.git
   cd mini-crm-dashboard
Install dependencies

bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
Run the application

bash
streamlit run app.py
Open your browser

text
http://localhost:8501
