ğŸ¯ How to Use
Adding Customers
Navigate to the Customers page

Fill out the form in the sidebar

Click "Add Customer"

Customer appears instantly in the list

Managing Customers
Search: Use the search bar to find specific customers

Edit: Click the edit button next to any customer

Delete: Click delete and confirm the action

View: Switch between table and card views

Analytics & Insights
Visit the Analytics page for visual insights

View customer distribution by industry

Track customer growth over time

Analyze company statistics

ğŸš€ Deployment
Streamlit Cloud (Recommended)
Push your code to GitHub

Visit share.streamlit.io

Connect your GitHub repository

Deploy with one click!

Other Platforms
Heroku: Use Procfile and requirements.txt

AWS: Deploy with Elastic Beanstalk

Docker: Containerize your application

ğŸ”§ Configuration
Environment Variables
Create a .streamlit/secrets.toml file for sensitive data:

toml
[general]
COMPANY_NAME = "Your Company"
Customization
Modify colors in the CSS section of app.py

Add new customer fields in the form

Extend analytics with additional charts

