ğŸ› Troubleshooting
Common Issues
Module Not Found Errors:

bash
pip install --upgrade streamlit pandas
Port Already in Use:

bash
streamlit run app.py --server.port 8502
Data Not Persisting:

Check file permissions for customers.json

Ensure proper read/write access

